    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Develop a templete for generating MDG-related disaggregated statistics and indicators developed:\r\n\t\r\n\t\tApply the template to the latest ppopulation and housing census data and produce in selected countries and disseminate disaggregated stastistics;\r\n\t\r\n\t\tDevelop a methodology for generating estimates of selected health or education-related MDG Indicators;\r\n\t\r\n\t\tApply the SAE methodology in producing estimates in selected countries;\r\n\t\r\n\t\tConduct a regional inception workshop to share knowledge and good practices among member states and arrive at a common understanding among all country teams on the objectives, mtethodologies and implementation process of the initiative.\r\n\t\r\n\t\tConduct a regional training /workshop to share knowledge  and experience on census data tabulation, small area estimation and master sample construction  among countries and to plan possible future capacity development work on data disaggregation."
      },
